<h3>Column start and column span</h3>
<p>The Bolt Grid is built on the concept of column start and column span, this allows the user to have full control of the grid layout.</p>

<h3>Common usage</h3>

{% set item_aside %}
  {% include '@bolt-components-placeholder/placeholder.twig' with {
    text: 'Aside',
  } only %}
{% endset %}

{% set item_main %}
  {% include '@bolt-components-placeholder/placeholder.twig' with {
    text: 'Main',
  } only %}
{% endset %}

<p>Main content in the center (column start 3 and column span 8) with 2 asides.</p>
<div class="u-bolt-margin-bottom-medium">
  {% include '@bolt-components-grid/grid.twig' with {
    items: [
      {
        column_start: '1',
        column_span: '2',
        content: item_aside,
      },
      {
        column_start: '3',
        column_span: '8',
        content: item_main,
      },
      {
        column_start: '11',
        column_span: '2',
        content: item_aside,
      },
    ]
  } only %}
</div>

<p>Main content with an aside (column start 9 and column span 4).</p>
<div class="u-bolt-margin-bottom-large">
  {% include '@bolt-components-grid/grid.twig' with {
    items: [
      {
        column_start: '1',
        column_span: '8',
        content: item_main,
      },
      {
        column_start: '9',
        column_span: '4',
        content: item_aside,
      },
    ]
  } only %}
</div>


<h3>Row start and row span</h3>
<p>Row start and row span are also available, they are for less common layouts.</p>

{% set item_row %}
  {% include '@bolt-components-placeholder/placeholder.twig' with {
    text: 'Row',
  } only %}
{% endset %}

<div class="u-bolt-margin-bottom-large">
  {% include '@bolt-components-grid/grid.twig' with {
    items: [
      {
        column_start: '1',
        column_span: '4',
        row_start: '1',
        content: item_row,
      },
      {
        column_start: '1',
        column_span: '1',
        row_start: '2',
        content: item_row,
      },
      {
        column_start: '1',
        column_span: '1',
        row_start: '3',
        content: item_row,
      },
      {
        column_start: '2',
        column_span: '3',
        row_start: '2',
        row_span: '2',
        content: 'Start at column 2 and row 2 and span 2 rows.',
        attributes: {
          class: [
            't-bolt-dark',
            'u-bolt-padding-small',
          ]
        },
      },
      {
        column_start: '5',
        column_span: '9',
        row_start: '1',
        content: item_row,
      },
      {
        column_start: '5',
        column_span: '9',
        row_start: '2',
        content: item_row,
      },
      {
        column_start: '5',
        column_span: '9',
        row_start: '3',
        content: item_row,
      },
    ]
  } only %}
</div>

<h3>All possible start and span options</h3>
